            <p style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 100;" class="story">
                <!-- <b style="font-size: large;">LORE: </b> -->
                Udyr is more than a man—he is a vessel for the untamed power of primal Freljordian animal spirits. 
                When tapping into their bestial natures, he can harness different strengths, channeling untold speed, resilience, and brutal ferocity. 
                With their combined might, Udyr will turn back all those who dare to harm the natural order of the world.
            </p>
            <h3 style="margin-top: 8%; text-align: center; font-size: 25px;filter:drop-shadow(5);" id="buildStory">
                Build your story!
            </h3>
            <!-- insert a text box and a button that says make your story-->
            <input class="inputBox" type="text" name="story" placeholder="What is your name?" style="margin-top: 5%;"
                required="required" id="inputHider">
            <a class="button1" font-size="25" id="disableMe">Away we go!</a>
            <!-- disable button1 after it is clicked-->

            <!-- make an api call when the button is pressed, use the input as query for the api call-->
            <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.0.min.js"></script>
            <script>
                // make an api call when the button is pressed, use the input as query for the api call
                $(".button1").click(function () {
                    const btn = document.getElementById('disableMe');
                    btn.style.display = 'none';
                    const input = document.getElementById('inputHider');
                    input.style.display = 'none';
                    const story = document.getElementById('buildStory');
                    story.style.display = 'none';
                    var name = $(".inputBox").val();
                    console.log(name);
                    if (name.length = 0 || name === undefined || name === null || name === "") {
                        alert("Please enter a name");
                    } else {
                        console.log(name);
                        $(".story").append('<br><br>');
                        var i = 0;
                        var txt = `${name} had always been alone. He was born into a wealthy family, but his parents never had time for him. His only friends were the toys his parents bought him to keep him quiet. He loved his toys, and he loved playing with them. 
But he always felt like something was missing. One day, his parents brought him a new toy. 
It was a marionette, and it was the most beautiful thing ${name} had ever seen. He named the marionette Shaco, and he loved it immediately.
Shaco was the perfect friend: always happy, always willing to play. But one day, Shaco changed. 
He became cruel and sadistic, delighting in the misery of others. ${name} was distraught, but he couldn’t bear to part with his friend. 
So he kept Shaco close, even as the marionette’s darkness consumed him. 
Now, ${name} is a puppet of Shaco’s, forced to do the demon jester’s bidding. 
He has lost everything, but he still clings to the hope that one day he will be reunited with his beloved friend.`; /* The text */
                        var speed = 1; /* The speed/duration of the effect in milliseconds */
                        // make the color of the text change
                        function typeWriter() {
                            if (i < txt.length) {
                                // make the color of the text change
                                $(".story").append(txt.charAt(i));
                                i++;
                                setTimeout(typeWriter, speed);
                            }
                        }
                        function endingText() {
                            $(".story").append('<br><br>');
                            $(".story").append('<b>This story was generated with GPT3!</b>');
                            $(".story").append('<br><br><br>');
                            $(".story").append('<a class="button1" font-size="25" id="enableMe"href="/champions/udyr">Make your story with Udyr ➤</a>');
                        }

                        typeWriter();
                        setTimeout(endingText, 5000);
                    }
                });
            </script>
